 \ \sin(\pi - x) \ = \ \sin x \ . 
 \ x \ , 
 \ \cos(\pi - x) \ = \ -\cos x \ . 
 \ \tan x \ = \ \frac{\sin x}{\cos x} \ , 
 \ \tan (\pi - x) \ = \ \frac{\sin (\pi - x)}{\cos (\pi - x)} \ = \ \frac{\sin x}{-\cos x} \ = \ -\tan x \ \ . 
 \\ 
 \ \tan (\pi + x) \ = \ \frac{\sin (\pi + x)}{\cos (\pi + x)} \ = \ \frac{-\sin x}{-\cos x} \ = \ \tan x \ \ . 
 \\ 
