 \ x \ 
 \ \frac{\pi}{2} - x \ . 
 \ \tan (\frac{\pi}{2} - x) \ = \ \frac{\sin (\frac{\pi}{2} - x )}{\cos (\frac{\pi}{2} - x)} \ = \ \frac{\cos x}{\sin x} \ = \ \frac{1}{\tan x} \ = \ \cot x \ \ . 
